data.name: ReadInterstateCase
data.value: select top(1) LOCAL_FIPS_STATE, LOCAL_FIPS_COUNTY, LOCAL_FIPS_LOCATIO, OTHER_FIPS_STATE, OTHER_FIPS_COUNTY, OTHER_FIPS_LOCATIO, TRANS_SERIAL_NBR, ACTION_CODE, FUNCTIONAL_TYPE_CO, TRANSACTION_DATE, KS_CASE_ID, INTERSTATE_CASE_ID, ACTION_REASON_CODE, ACTION_RESOLUTION, ATTACHMENTS_IND, CASE_DATA_IND, AP_IDENTIFICATION, AP_LOCATE_DATA_IND, PARTICIPANT_DATA_I, ORDER_DATA_IND, COLLECTION_DATA_IN, INFORMATION_IND, SENT_DATE, SENT_TIME, DUE_DATE, OVERDUE_IND, DATE_RECEIVED, TIME_RECEIVED, ATTACHMNTS_DUE_DTE, INTERSTATE_FORMS_P, CASE_TYPE, CASE_STATUS, PAYMENT_MAILING_AD, PAYMENT_ADDRESS_LI, PAYMENT_CITY, PAYMENT_STATE, PAYMENT_ZIP_CODE_5, PAYMENT_ZIP_CODE_4, CONTACT_NAME_LAST, CONTACT_NAME_FIRST, CONTACT_NAME_MIDDL, CONTACT_NAME_SUFFI, CONTACT_ADDR_LINE1, CONTACT_ADDR_LINE2, CONTACT_CITY, CONTACT_STATE, CONTACT_ZIP_CODE_5, CONTACT_ZIP_CODE_4, CONTACT_PHONE_NUM, ASSN_DEACT_DT, ASSN_DEACT_IND, LAST_DEFER_DT, MEMO from CKT_INTERST_CASE where (TRANS_SERIAL_NBR = @transSerialNbr) and (TRANSACTION_DATE = @transactionDate)

data.name: ReadInterstateCaseAssignment
data.value: select DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, ICS_DATE, ICS_NO from CKT_ASSGN_INT_CASE where (@icsNo = ICS_NO) and (@icsDate = ICS_DATE) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE > @discontinueDate)

data.name: ReadInterstateParticipant
data.value: select CCA_TRANSACTION_DT, SYS_GENERATED_ID, CCA_TRANS_SER_NUM, NAME_LAST, NAME_FIRST, NAME_MIDDLE, NAME_SUFFIX, DATE_OF_BIRTH, SSN, SEX, RACE, RELATIONSHIP, STATUS, DEPENDENT_RELATION, ADDRESS_LINE_1, ADDRESS_LINE_2, CITY, [STATE], ZIP_CODE_5, ZIP_CODE_4, EMP_ADDRESS_LINE_1, EMP_ADDRESS_LINE_2, EMPLOYER_CITY, EMPLOYER_STATE, EMP_ZIP_CODE_5, EMP_ZIP_CODE_4, EMPLOYER_NAME, EMPLOYER_EIN, ADDR_VERIFIED_DATE, EMP_VERIFIED_DATE, WORK_PHONE, WORK_AREA_CODE, PLACE_OF_BIRTH, CHILD_STATE_OF_RES, CHILD_PATER_STATUS, EMP_CONFIRMED_IND, ADDR_CONFIRMED_IND from CKT_INTERST_PART where (@ccaTransactionDt = CCA_TRANSACTION_DT) and (@ccaTransSerNum = CCA_TRANS_SER_NUM) order by SYS_GENERATED_ID

data.name: ReadInterstateRequest
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST with(readuncommitted) where IDENTIFIER = @identifier

data.name: ReadInterstateRequestHistory
data.value: select INT_GENERATED_ID, CREATED_TSTAMP, TRANSACTION_SERIAL, TRANSACTION_DATE from CKT_INT_RQST_HIST with(readuncommitted) where (TRANSACTION_SERIAL = @transactionSerial) and (TRANSACTION_DATE = @transactionDate)

data.name: ReadInterstateSupportOrder
data.value: select CCA_TRANSACTION_DT, SYS_GENERATED_ID, CCA_TRAN_SER_NUM, FIPS_STATE, FIPS_COUNTY, FIPS_LOCATION, NUMBER, ORDER_FILING_DATE, TYPE, DEBT_TYPE, PAYMENT_FREQ, AMOUNT_ORDERED, EFFECTIVE_DATE, END_DATE, CANCEL_DATE, ARREARS_FREQ, ARREARS_FRQ_AMT, ARREARS_TOTAL_AMT, ARRS_AFDC_FROM_DTE, ARRS_AFDC_THRU_DTE, ARREARS_AFDC_AMT, ARR_NAFDC_FROM_DTE, ARR_NAFDC_THRU_DTE, ARR_NAFDC_AMT, FOST_CARE_FROM_DTE, FOST_CARE_THRU_DTE, FOSTER_CARE_AMOUNT, MEDICAL_FROM_DATE, MEDICAL_THRU_DATE, MEDICAL_AMOUNT, MEDICAL_ORDERED_IN, TRIBUNAL_CASE_NUM, DATE_OF_LAST_PAY, CNTRL_ORDER_FLAG, NEW_ORDER_FLAG, DOCKET_NUMBER, LEGAL_ACTION_ID from CKT_INTERST_SUP_OR where (@ccaTransactionDt = CCA_TRANSACTION_DT) and (@ccaTranSerNum = CCA_TRAN_SER_NUM) order by SYS_GENERATED_ID

data.name: UpdateInterstateCaseAssignment
data.value: update CKT_ASSGN_INT_CASE set DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst where (CREATED_TIMESTAMP = @createdTimestamp) and (SPD_ID = @spdId) and (OFF_ID = @offId) and (OSP_CODE = @ospCode) and (OSP_DATE = @ospDate) and (ICS_DATE = @icsDate) and (ICS_NO = @icsNo)
